title: Multi-vehicle crash on M621 - lane closed
text:
There is queuing traffic on the M621 eastbound following a multi-vehicle accident.
Once lane has been closed following the collision between J3, A653 (City Centre) & J5, Tunstal Road.
WYP Contact Centre @WYP_CCC Follow There has been an accident on the M621. Our RPU are at scene and dealing. This is J4 going in the direction of Holbeck and the city centre
